00:16:34,460 --> 00:16:37,530
Mom, I'm sorry I didn't tell you first, 

274
00:16:37,530 --> 00:16:39,530
but I'm not good at teaching. 

275
00:16:39,530 --> 00:16:43,550
I became a teacher because dad's a teacher,
and I thought it'd be a nice job for a woman. 

276
00:16:43,550 --> 00:16:48,290
Getting up early is really hard,
and I'm not the teaching type. 

277
00:16:48,290 --> 00:16:51,210
What am I going to do with you, huh? 

278
00:16:51,210 --> 00:16:55,090
Can't you see how everyone in the country is dying to become a teacher? 

279
00:16:55,090 --> 00:16:57,270
It's not everyone in the country. 

280
00:16:57,270 --> 00:17:00,380
Have you forgotten how everyone became envious when you became a teacher? 

281
00:17:00,380 --> 00:17:02,380
It wasn't everyone. 

282
00:17:04,750 --> 00:17:06,410
When will you become that writer thing? 

283
00:17:06,410 --> 00:17:07,780
You answer her. 

284
00:17:07,780 --> 00:17:10,870
I don't know. You'll need luck. 

285
00:17:10,870 --> 00:17:12,270
It's kind of impossible. 

286
00:17:12,270 --> 00:17:13,620
That's so sad. 

287
00:17:13,620 --> 00:17:14,870
I'll make it happen as soon as possible. 

288
00:17:14,870 --> 00:17:16,060
Quit! 

289
00:17:17,180 --> 00:17:18,350
Oh, man! 

290
00:17:18,980 --> 00:17:21,100
Put yourself in Gwangbak's shoes. 

291
00:17:21,100 --> 00:17:22,760
Afraid of you finding about it, 

292
00:17:22,760 --> 00:17:27,020
