293
00:17:27,020 --> 00:17:29,700
Why would you do it if you're so scared! 

294
00:17:30,670 --> 00:17:34,700
Wait a minute, you knew about this, didn't you? 

295
00:17:35,540 --> 00:17:36,970
Huh? 

296
00:17:36,970 --> 00:17:38,630
Uh, no. 

297
00:17:39,710 --> 00:17:41,590
Did dad know about it? 

298
00:17:41,590 --> 00:17:44,670
Well, actually... 

299
00:17:44,670 --> 00:17:46,220
I'm sorry, dad. 

300
00:17:47,170 --> 00:17:49,210
Oh, man... 

301
00:17:49,210 --> 00:17:50,780
How could you? 

302
00:17:50,780 --> 00:17:54,140
When your daughter goes mad and starts talking nonsense, 

303
00:17:54,140 --> 00:17:56,060
you should be telling her right from wrong! 

304
00:17:56,060 --> 00:17:59,260
Instead, you lead her down the wrong path? 

305
00:17:59,260 --> 00:18:01,400
Must you be so cruel? 

306
00:18:01,400 --> 00:18:03,150
She says it's her dream! 

307
00:18:03,150 --> 00:18:04,600
Stop torturing him. 

308
00:18:04,600 --> 00:18:08,230
Why are you torturing my child when it's your child's fault? 

309
00:18:08,230 --> 00:18:10,130
I'm not holding the memorial ceremony. 

310
00:18:10,130 --> 00:18:12,470
- What?
- She's not doing the ceremony. 

311
00:18:12,470 --> 00:18:14,670
How dare you! 

312
00:18:40,360 --> 00:18:41,400
Mr. Ko! 

313
00:18:44,580 --> 00:18:47,050
The creditors were here. 

314
00:18:47,050 --> 00:18:48,390
What do we do? 

315
00:18:53,450 --> 00:18:55,430
That hurts! 

316
00:18:55,430 --> 00:18:57,170
Ouch. 

317
00:18:58,330 --> 00:18:59,520
What are you laughing at? 

318
00:19:00,150 --> 00:19:02,310
Why you little... 

319
00:19:02,310 --> 00:19:03,760
Let me go! That really hurts. 

320
00:19:03,760 --> 00:19:06,500
Then be quiet and follow me. 

321
00:19:07,350 --> 00:19:11,430
It hurts, let me go, let me go. Ouch. 

322
00:19:14,310 --> 00:19:16,800
Let's talk, man to man. 

323
00:19:16,800 --> 00:19:18,660
Why do you walk around during class? 

324
00:19:18,660 --> 00:19:20,000
Don't you get tired? 

325
00:19:20,000 --> 00:19:21,790
I don't really get tired. 

326
00:19:21,790 --> 00:19:24,430
Bring your parents in for a conference. 

327
00:19:24,430 --> 00:19:27,160
It'd be better to just talk to me. 

328
00:19:28,760 --> 00:19:31,420
I can't have a conversation with you! 

329
00:19:31,420 --> 00:19:33,080
I can talk to you just fine. 

330
00:19:34,550 --> 00:19:36,710
You're aging your teacher! 

331
00:19:38,270 --> 00:19:40,170
He's been old! 

332
00:19:41,580 --> 00:19:43,220
He's been old? 

333
00:19:43,220 --> 00:19:44,650
I can't believe you said that! 

334
00:19:44,650 --> 00:19:46,680
You can't talk to him. 

335
00:19:46,680 --> 00:19:48,340
It's impossible to communicate with him! 

336
00:19:48,340 --> 00:19:49,750
Go. 

337
00:19:49,750 --> 00:19:52,000
Bring one of your parents tomorrow! 

338
00:19:52,000 --> 00:19:54,310
Don't get your hopes up. 

339
00:20:03,030 --> 00:20:04,430
Mr. Kim, 

340
00:20:05,430 --> 00:20:10,550
