535
00:32:54,400 --> 00:32:59,010
His sister in law won't stop picking on him. 

536
00:32:59,010 --> 00:33:06,060
Honey, you know Bong is the best son in the world, don't you? 

537
00:33:06,060 --> 00:33:12,450
He brings me back to life whenever I get sick, 

538
00:33:12,450 --> 00:33:16,390
he always does that. 

539
00:33:16,390 --> 00:33:19,740
He won't let me come and meet you. 

540
00:33:19,740 --> 00:33:23,330
And our youngest son. 

541
00:33:23,330 --> 00:33:29,580
I'm so grateful you gave him to me before leaving. 

542
00:33:29,580 --> 00:33:32,760
Oh, he plays cards with me. 

