We forgot what we did and blamed it on constipation. 

556
00:34:12,540 --> 00:34:17,300
It was so much trouble, worse than the Korean War. 

557
00:34:17,670 --> 00:34:20,540
Egh, hyo, hyo, hyo. 

558
