Coming! 

560
00:34:26,380 --> 00:34:28,420
Sis, do the dishes later and come eat with us. 

561
00:34:28,420 --> 00:34:29,750
I'll just finish this up. 

562
00:34:29,750 --> 00:34:32,030
I'll have to do it sooner or later. 

563
00:34:32,030 --> 00:34:33,090
Okay. 

564
00:34:34,320 --> 00:34:35,750
Uncle, I need to talk to you. 

565
00:34:35,750 --> 00:34:37,750
I get scared whenever you say that. 

566
