569
00:34:44,070 --> 00:34:45,170
You won't have anyone to hang with. 

570
00:34:45,170 --> 00:34:48,000
Heo Sedal! I can't believe he said that. 

571
00:34:48,000 --> 00:34:49,370
And you believe him? 

572
