576
00:35:00,180 --> 00:35:01,450
Where are your husbands? 

577
00:35:01,450 --> 00:35:03,450
Why aren't they here? 

578
00:35:03,450 --> 00:35:05,220
They're all busy. 

579
00:35:05,220 --> 00:35:07,480
Even so! 

580
00:35:08,010 --> 00:35:10,080
You have to feel sorry for your father. 

581
00:35:10,080 --> 00:35:12,820
He has nobody to do this for him. 

582
00:35:13,560 --> 00:35:14,940
He has me. 

583
00:35:15,830 --> 00:35:20,370
Oh, I forgot all about you! 

584
00:35:20,370 --> 00:35:23,270
You're not the only woman who had a son at an old age. 

585
00:35:23,270 --> 00:35:24,760
I've suffered, too. 

586
00:35:24,760 --> 00:35:26,490
Giving birth at an old age must run in the family. 

587
00:35:26,490 --> 00:35:29,020
Why don't you have one, too? 

588
00:35:29,020 --> 00:35:30,790
Don't! It's too much trouble. 

589
00:35:30,790 --> 00:35:32,110
Just raise the two you have right now well. 

590
00:35:32,110 --> 00:35:33,410
Oh, don't worry. 

591
00:35:33,410 --> 00:35:36,810
