00:35:47,640 --> 00:35:49,320
You have problems with your dentures? 

596
00:35:49,320 --> 00:35:50,150
No. 

597
00:35:50,150 --> 00:35:52,150
Why would you ask your granddaughter that? 

598
00:35:52,150 --> 00:35:53,280
You have a son right here. 

599
00:35:53,280 --> 00:35:54,950
I'll get you new ones. 

600
00:35:54,950 --> 00:35:58,660
Tell her that after you actually do it. 

601
00:35:58,660 --> 00:35:59,570
Yes, sir. 

602
00:35:59,570 --> 00:36:00,850
Uncle, have some beer. 

603
00:36:03,490 --> 00:36:06,060
Your face changes every time I see you. 

604
