They even have ones that are 50 cents. 

620
00:36:48,160 --> 00:36:51,010
Hobak's husband doesn't make money like Minjung does. 

621
00:36:51,010 --> 00:36:53,750
It's the thought that counts, not the money. 

622
00:36:55,680 --> 00:36:57,520
What's Sedal been up to? 

623
00:36:57,520 --> 00:36:59,190
Is he ever getting a job? 

624
00:37:00,050 --> 00:37:02,900
