Sedal won't help, so I've been trying so hard to save every penny... 

1075
01:02:33,370 --> 01:02:35,900
I'm not going to think of you as my daughter! 

1076
01:02:35,900 --> 01:02:37,610
Ugh! How could anyone love you? 

1077
01:02:37,610 --> 01:02:40,750
I feel really bad, so I can't say hello properly. 

1078
01:02:40,750 --> 01:02:42,650
Why don't we go to a police station? 

1079
01:02:43,320 --> 01:02:44,380
You said you wanted to go to a police station. 

1080
01:02:44,380 --> 01:02:46,820
I think I've seen you before. 

1081
01:02:46,820 --> 01:02:48,440
That's way too obvious. 

1082
01:02:48,440 --> 01:02:50,110
I saw something weird today. 

1083
01:02:50,110 --> 01:02:51,540
Why? What was it? 

1084
01:02:51,540 --> 01:02:52,920
Isn't that your brother in law? 

1085
01:02:52,920 --> 01:02:54,500
Do you know what next Saturday is? 

1086
01:02:54,500 --> 01:02:56,140
I told you, my mom's 60th birthday. 

1087
01:02:56,140 --> 01:02:58,230
It's my mother's first memorial service. 

1088
01:02:58,230 --> 01:02:59,450
Can't we do it another day? 

1089
01:02:59,450 --> 01:03:00,100
What's this? 

1090
01:03:00,100 --> 01:03:02,060
Tell your father to come and eat. 

